snippet.title: Darksiders II: Deathinitive Edition | PlayStation 5 & Xbox Series X|S Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
The war between Heaven and Hell continues on PlayStation 5 and Xbox Series X|S on October 15th!

DISCLAIMER: We would like to state that the Darksiders teaser of our 2024 digital showcase is NOT in reference to the subsequent announcement of Darksiders II Deathinitive for PS5 and Xbox Series S|X.

----
Website: https://darksiders.com
Facebook: https://facebook.com/Darksiders
Discord: https://discord.gg/darksiders

#Darksiders #Deathinitive
